{"tid":1590463,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭WH之法荷遊","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T07:37:21.000Z","uid":320615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d071bf4241d8c3492ab28cfe42ad7fd615bcaac0","tid":1590463,"uid":320615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"今年一月同另一半起程咗去紐西蘭。<br />\n人傑地靈，要山得山，要水得水，要羊得羊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生活咗大半年，身體都好咗唔少，雖然本身身體都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旅程中我同另一半8月中決定回荷蘭探親兼遊法國，本身幻想成個旅程會好撚開心⋯⋯點知係法國俾人偷撚左個護照，依家滯留緊係荷蘭等緊我本BNO。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲係NZ WH或者歐遊中分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或對紐西蘭WH有野想知，我好樂意答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59b3d78fca8071771a06c889413e4009616993f","tid":1590463,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"08b1cc1626686a8b55702f83d53c86f20894db4b","tid":1590463,"uid":271766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"哈囉絲打 薪火見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我反而想知你wh個visa點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你快啲拎返本BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dca9657da194161c27a9dea3e8a4afb1a2249d","tid":1590463,"uid":320615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote